      "content": {
        "title": "Related Rates",
        "definition": "Problems in which several quantities vary with time and are linked by an equation; differentiating implicitly with respect to time relates their rates of change.",
        "summary": "Related rates apply the chain rule to dynamic geometric and physical situations such as expanding balloons, sliding ladders, and filling tanks."
